data.title: Prince George's County, Maryland
data.meta_description: Prince George's County is located in the U.S. state of Maryland, bordering the eastern portion of Washington, D.C.
data.text:
Courage, Compassion, and Professionalism

We celebrate the graduation of the County’s newest firefighters and paramedics, Career Recruit School 67! These graduates completed a rigorous training program and are ready to save lives.

Learn More

Discover Our Eco-Friendly Transit Revolution!

The County was awarded $25.4M for green transit! We are creating a cleaner, greener, and more efficient public transit system.

Learn How

Summer is Getting Hot!

The County has set up cooling centers to provide residents with a safe place to escape the heat. The centers have air conditioning and water for those without access to cool environments.

Find a Cooling Center

Summer Prince George's with the Washington Nationals

Adventure begins at your library! Read, stream, and get social with the Library and the Washington Nationals through August 15.

Explore

County Highlights

Stuff TheBus School Supply Drive

Help students prepare for the new school year with new bookbags and school supplies. Join the Department of Public Works & Transportation and help us Stuff TheBus!

Stay Safe in the Water This Summer!

Do you know how to swim? Prepare yourself and your family for a safe swimming season. Get tips and best practices to keep you and your family safe in, on, and around the water.
